	<Title>
		Cupping therapy: Can it relieve fibromyalgia pain?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Cupping is one of many alternative therapies used to help relieve fibromyalgia pain.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is there any evidence that cupping therapy relieves fibromyalgia pain?
	</Question>
